'''Shrike Squadron''' served the [[Suprema]] of [[Mandalore/Legends|Mandalore]], flying a variant of [[Airspeeder/Legends|airspeeders]].

Stationed at the [[City of Bone]], the [[Squadron/Legends|squadron]] was destroyed when it flew into the inner wall of the [[Slavery/Legends|slave]] city while trying to avoid the rapidly closing door shut by [[Tobbi Dala]]. Their crash began a chain reaction of fuel that eventually destroyed the city.

